{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PointerEvent.twist","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/twist","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Pointer_events\">Pointer events</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/isPrimary\"><code>isPrimary</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerId\"><code>pointerId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerType\"><code>pointerType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pressure\"><code>pressure</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tangentialPressure\"><code>tangentialPressure</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltX\"><code>tiltX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltY\"><code>tiltY</code></a></li><li><em><code>twist</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/getCoalescedEvents\"><code>getCoalescedEvents()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Pointer Events に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/releasePointerCapture\"><code>Element.releasePointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/setPointerCapture\"><code>Element.setPointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/maxTouchPoints\"><code>Navigator.maxTouchPoints</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>twist</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、ポインタ（例えばペン/スタイラス）の主軸を中心とした時計回りの回転を度数で表します。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>twist</em> = <em>pointerEvent</em>.twist;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>トランスデューサ（ポインタ）に適用される、ねじれの量を度数で表す <code>long</code> 値。 値の範囲は <code>0</code> から <code>359</code> です。 <code>twist</code> を報告しないデバイスの場合、値は <code>0</code> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/pointerdown\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">pointerdown</a></code> イベントが発生すると、イベントの <code>twist</code> プロパティの値に応じてさまざまな関数が呼び出されます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>someElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'pointerdown'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>twist <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ねじれなし</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">process_no_twist</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// デフォルト</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">process_twist</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/pointerevents2/#dom-pointerevent-twist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Pointer Events – Level 2<br><small lang=\"ja\">twist の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PointerEvent.twist","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/twist/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch/force\"><code>Touch.force</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"PointerEvent インターフェイスの twist 読み取り専用プロパティは、ポインタ（例えばペン/スタイラス）の主軸を中心とした時計回りの回転を度数で表します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PointerEvent.twist","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/pointerevent/twist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/pointerevent/twist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent","title":"PointerEvent"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/twist","title":"PointerEvent.twist"}],"pageTitle":"PointerEvent.twist - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}